message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to discuss the product with you. I think it's a great fit for you, and I'm willing to make a one-time offer to sweeten the deal. I'm willing to sell the product to you for $12000. This is a great price, considering the value it will bring to your business. I think you'll really love it, and I'm confident you won't find a better deal anywhere else. What do you think?
